title: What's behind Catalonia's independence movement?
description:
We went to the heart of the Catalonia region to speak with the man behind the independence movement. 
The government of Spain considers him the most dangerous man in Europe.

Al Jazeera's John Hendren sat down with Catalonia President Carles Puigdemont and asked him why he favours secession.
